data.description: Your family will love this beautifully appointed home in sought after Fox Ridge East Newnan. This spacious home boasts a large formal living and dining room, with a sizable den and kitchen for entertaining. Upstairs has 3 bedrooms, 3 full baths, plus a bonus room and an office that could be 5th and 6th bedrooms. The Master bedroom has a sizeable walk-in closet with plenty of storage. Upgrades include LVP flooring, granite kitchen counter tops, and 1st floor guest or secondary master suite. The fenced back yard is divided into two sections connected by a gate with a lovely wooded area in the 2nd fenced portion. Home is convenient to Peachtree City, Piedmont Hospital, I-85 and Hartsfield International Airport. Neighborhood amenities include a community pool and tennis court.
